### 5. 用户 A 登录 (第 5 次，扣减令牌至 0，预期 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
x-forwarded-for: {{testIp}}

{
  "username": "user_limit_a",
  "password": "wrong_password_a"
